{"tid":968964,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［環保L入黎］是咁的 我「又」 搞左個時裝品牌","createTime":"2019-01-04T16:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T18:02:30.000Z","uid":21863,"like":60,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"93dd92d5542e49c8961842fdfb113c560f5cbf34","tid":968964,"uid":21863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的，見近排咁多人整時裝品牌，我都心血來潮係屋企一個人設計左件衫。<br />\n<br />\n既然近期環保風氣盛行，我一於為所有環保人士設計呢件連登狗pocket tee 宣揚走飲筒意識！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcqdOLb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcqdOLb.png&h=3f866d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n著住去食m記、大家樂就岩晒，見到經理真係無比飲筒，即刻可以拉低個pocket 支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHYSjRR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHYSjRR.png&h=f77d3d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，既然有設計，咁都要整返個品牌名同logo。我決定簡個潮d既名 &mdash; 9ITEM<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmdCvYP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmdCvYP.png&h=1eceb997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小個logo，我都花左半個鐘設計。為左表現文藝復興時期的美術哲學，過程中參考大師達文西繪畫蒙羅麗莎時使用1：1.618的黃金比例，。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sd9Rs02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSd9Rs02.png&h=e0f62071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都照舊講下挫折...呢個idea 其實係我今日係m記飲可樂無飲筒，敏感牙齒激發我諗出黎。當中既痛楚同辛酸，相信好多巴絲都感受過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後，如果你想支持呢個品牌/睇多d創作，可以follow facebook 同 instagram<br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/9item/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F9item%2F&d=9qXlY%2BjSbx5suXWKSvYojTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=29bc42a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/9item/</a><br />\nfb： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/9ITEM.OFFICIAL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F9ITEM.OFFICIAL&d=9qXlY%2BjSbx5suXWKSvYojTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=101716e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/9ITEM.OFFICIAL</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f906a281dd2e87e038f15cca43dab65ea05871f","tid":968964,"uid":176051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"支持隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdefa3386b8590f35c0e2027832f0cc75da59bbf","tid":968964,"uid":33147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"又玩 繼續bin<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c6447fa39babd3ed7cc2782e7373e55ec6869b","tid":968964,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15fb6d1e92051cb5bf78320fb33ab639e2ec09ea","tid":968964,"uid":28307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd7c2dab9300f5ccfd1287fdfb37e6cf36413ad","tid":968964,"uid":223164,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96c6447fa39babd3ed7cc2782e7373e55ec6869b","tid":968964,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"我同我拍檔都有討論過呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe63b321440b0ce5adf4e53b0794ca6f54a6cd4","tid":968964,"uid":228917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:19:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"572694a1e6f0c9c8fa0f564b43d72b5887cbf91e","tid":968964,"uid":156203,"like":16,"dislike":7,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"公仔抄